metadata.name: Joe's Club Bronze Tier
metadata.description: As a Michelin Bib Gourmand Restaurant pioneer in Chicago, Joe’s Imports is blending the interests of wine lovers and Web3 enthusiasts for exclusive in-person and virtual community experiences. We are dedicating the Joe’s Imports NFT to honor our beloved Joe Fiely, or “Smiley Joe Fiely,” as customers warm-heartedly called our late and beloved Wine Director at Scott Harris Hospitality.
